title: The Rollinator
description: Chep is so good at moss-marbles, no one wants to play him anymore! No one except Sumush who reveals himself to be a tough competitor. To Chep's disbelief, Sumush keeps on winning. But Lilit and Mush-Mush convince their friend not to give up. Chep decides to play his favourite moss-marble: the Rollinator. The one marble he never risked playing before.

title: Huggbees
description: The Brain teams up with The Lobe, so the Titans enlist the help of Freakazoid to stop them.

title: Fashion Forward
description: When the Fashionistas launch a new line of brainwashing clothing, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop the fashion trend before it's too late.

title: Music
description: Bing, Sula and Pando are making music with Flop and Amma. Everyone has their own instruments, but they all want the drum. Pando gets to go first, but what will happen when it's time to swap and Sula gets the drum next?

title: Guardian of the Unikingdom
description: Hawkodile insists the Unikingdom is more dangerous than it looks and sets out to prove it by taking his friends on bodyguard patrol.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: Haunted House/Two of a Kind
description: Haunted House: Rumor has it that there's a haunted building in Los Volmos, and the Awesome Brawlers are on the case! Who doesn't like a good ghost hunt, plus capturing a ghost on camera should make Awesome Brawlers' next video a huge success!/Two of a Kind: Veronica Venegas is doing a special report on the Awesome brawlers own: Lightening! The special report takes a back seat when Lightening is challenged to a brawl. Lightening uses this brawl the perfect opportunity to rollout his new Bakugan partner: Tretorous.

title: Ant We All Just Get Along
description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

title: Prepare for the Worst
description: Axel and Bobbie Blobby skip out on Sarge's disaster-prep drills, leaving enough of a gap in the team's defenses for a crow to swoop in and snatch Sarge! Feeling responsible, Axel leads the team on a search-and-rescue mission.

title: Water, Water Everywhere
description: Grumpy doesn't believe Funshine's warning that an invisible "Big Blob in the sky" is stealing water from a Whiffle garden -- he has pulled too many practical jokes before. To save the garden and his own credibility, Funshine must discover the truth of the menacing "Big Blob."

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Elly's Shoes
description: Elly gets a fancy new pair of dressing up shoes. She loves wearing them so much that she won't take them off, even to go to bed!

title: Last One There
description: When Unikitty accidentally invokes an ancient curse, the gang must beat Master Frown and Brock back to the castle before one of them literally turns into a rotten egg.

title: Professor Proofed
description: After the Professor's latest experiment goes awry, the girls become overprotective.

title: Folk Art Friends
description: When Vic and Val accidentally release some mischievous alebrije spirits, they must enlist the help of master mischief-maker HueHue to help catch them.

title: #HappyBirthdayZee
description: Zatanna makes a birthday wish that forces her to confront the dark side of her magic.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: Man of the House
description: Clarence's first night home alone spirals out of control, forcing Clarence and his pals to wage war against their own home security measures.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Power Tower
description: Muscle Man wants to win the bodybuilding competition at his gym.

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Winning at Whining
description: Vambre's challenge to Prohyas: Don't whine for the entirety of the next mission and you can have the Magisword we get at the end.

title: Secrets
description: Grandpa Max's mysterious past comes to light when Vilgax shows up on earth in search of the Omnitrix. And the family must work together to defeat him.

title: A Very Special Blossom/Daylight Savings
description: A Very Special Blossom: When the Professor wants an expensive gift for Father's Day, Blossom makes the mistake of taking what she can't afford instead of giving him a gift from the heart./Daylight Savings: The Powerpuff Girls are exhausted in school from saving Townsville past their bedtime. What will happen to their town when the girls are put on a curfew?

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wednesday - Part 4
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Neighborhood Grill
description: Clarence is so troubled by the sight of his teacher in a social setting outside of school, he can't stop himself from intruding on her doomed blind date.

title: The Bakugan Battle League/The Ancient Elder
description: The Bakugan Battle League: Benton Dusk is in the process of renovating a state of the art Bakugan Brawling stadium. When it comes to brawling, who better to test out the new arena than the Awesome Brawlers!/The Ancient Elder: Dan finds a new baku-bud in Gillitar. Well "bud" may be too strong a word, Dan and gang quickly learn that Gillator has a few "quirks" that keep him from fitting in with the rest of the Awesome Brawler's Bakugan.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Video Date
description: Panda is an avid e-dater, and when a lovely French woman matches with him and agrees to a video chat date. Panda and his brothers engineer the situation so Panda is able to show the best side of himself on the video chat, even if that side of him is completely exaggerated.

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: El es el Sheriff
description: iEl trío lucha por deshacerse del Rey cuando los acompaña como nuevo ayudante del sheriff por un día!

title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

title: Sheep Bears
description: The Bears get jobs as sheep herders on an idyllic farm.

title: The Heist
description: Richard discovers going into a bank whilst wearing a motorcycle helmet can land you in a lot of trouble.

title: Jail Break
description: Steven teams up with a new ally to rescue the Gems.

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Mo' Linguish/Oops, I Did It Again
description: Mo' Linguish: Mojo is sentenced to do community service for Townsville and begins teaching English at the Learning Annex. Soon everyone is speaking in circles like Mojo and the town comes to a standstill./Oops, I Did It Again: When the Professor realizes that all his successful experiments are actually just accidents, he sets out to do something brilliant on purpose!

title: Stakes Part 5: May I Come In?
description: Finn, Jake, Marceline, and PB set out to hunt down the Vamps. But who is hunting them?

title: Winner Takes All
description: After months of training for Luchador Day, Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo!

title: The Cast
description: After breaking his leg, Robin is confined to his room and spies through a telescope.

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Ben 24hrs
description: When Ben (and Gwen!) attempt to stay up all night for Adrenaland, the only theme park open 24/7, he not only fails to utilize his alien powers to stay awake, but his "sleep-alien-ing" causes disaster after disaster that Gwen must fix before things get way out of hand.

title: All Work and No Play
description: Having finally saved up and aquired an expensive toy race track, Apple and Onion are faced with one problem- there is no time to play with it.

title: Arachno Romance
description: After the girls feel slighted by the Professor when he gets a new girlfriend, the girls conspire to break them up.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Snarf's Day Off
description: Hey everyone, it's Snarf's monthly day off! That's right, this episode follows Snarf as he leaves Cats' Lair to get a needed vacation, by transforming into a normal cat and hanging out with a nice old lady on a farm! But his relaxing day is threatened when Snarf and the nice old lady cross paths with Mumm-Ra!

title: Conquista de Popularidad
description: Cuando Mao Mao descubre que no es tan popular como Colosal y Adorabat, sus amigos deciden reinventarlo en forma de un héroe más amable y tierno.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Todo Por Mao Mismo
description: El deseo de Mao Mao de convertirse en leyenda lo lleva a querer superarse a sí mismo una y otra vez. ¿Pero cuánto es suficiente?

title: P.L.O.T. Device 2: Beyond the Bored Dome
description: Dr. Fox reprograms the P.L.O.T. Device to only generate boring events, but the gang can't help but add drama and excitement to every scenario.

title: Enfermo
description: Cuando Mao Mao no quiere reconocer que está enfermo, pone al pueblo en peligro.

title: Popularity Conquest
description: When Mao Mao discovers that he is not as popular as Badgerclops and Adorabat, they decide to reinvent him as a kinder, cuddlier hero.

title: OTTO Motive
description: Kevin and Rook run into an old enemy from the Null Void while attending an intergalactic auto show. (Re-introducing classic Ben alien, Upgrade.)

title: Cereal Boxing
description: The kids become obsessed with getting the prizes from boxes of sugary cereal.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Recipe for Disaster
description: During Chefapalooza in the Rocky Mountains, three famous chefs and infamous bad-guys, The Tri-Chefta, hunt down Wildvine in hopes of creating their most exotic dish to date.

title: Punos Fuertes
description: Harto de perder cuando juega a los videojuegos contra su padre, Craig busca entrenarse en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Rigby Goes to Prom
description: Rigby asks Eileen to prom. But in order to get there, he has to sneak his Dad's car out of the garage and get it back in one piece.

title: Creek Talent Extravaganza
description: Hoping to help the Creek Daycare, Craig organizes a talent show.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Who Said That?
description: Daffy learns a bad word and must learn not to use it.

title: Fueygo Fest
description: When Vic and Val throw the biggest kid bash ever, they realize they aren't the party planners they thought they were as things start to fall apart.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Primo del Arroyo
description: Craig lleva a su primo Bryson al Arroyo, donde accidentalmente inicia una guerra de globos de agua.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Chloe and Ice Bear
description: On a day out with just Ice Bear, Chloe realizes Ice Bear only runs errands for his brothers. Determined to show him a fun day in the city, Chloe promises to help Ice Bear have a good time, even if it means staying  in a museum after it closes.

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Sliding/Spinning Webs
description: Lucas and Findley find an ice cube. When Lucas rides the ice cube in the sink and falls down the drain, a scared Findley rallies to save him./ Lucas questions his spider-hood when he can't spin a web properly.

title: The Art of Friendship
description: When Chanterelle sees how good Lilit is at painting, she offers to help her dig into her talent. But Lilit's art lessons conflict with the fun project she has been working on with Mush-Mush and Chep. And when she sees that her friends are having a great time without her, Lilit is seriously annoyed which her paintings start showing.

title: Wednesday - Part 3
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

title: Caillou's Cricket/Dog Dilemma/The Spider Issue
description: Caillou inadvertently brings a cricket in the house./When Sarah gets a new dog, Caillou is actually a little jealous./Caillou feels afraid of real spiders.

title: Looking After Flop
description: Flop is sick and Bing explains that he wants to take care of him. So Bing tells Flop to sit on the sofa and gives him a pillow and a blanket, and Hoppity Voosh too! But making honey lemon is tricky hard.

title: Growing Pains
description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

title: What's Ringette?/Rainy Day at the Beach/Caillou Climbs
description: Caillou and Leo want to play hockey./Caillou and his family are supposed to be enjoying a nice day./Mommy takes Caillou and Clementine to an indoor rock climbing wall.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

title: Big Scary Slide
description: There's lots of new exciting playground rides in Pocoyoland including one huge daring slide. Pocoyo is too scared to give it a go. Pocoyo bravely helps his friend and overcomes his fear.

title: The Magic of Spring
description: Bugs' failure as a magician turns to success when he experiences the true magic of nature.

title: Ben 24 Horas
description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: #AngerManagement
description: When Jess coerces Kara into addressing her anger management issues, Supergirl's superhero abilities become seriously compromised!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Blippi Learns Rainbow Colors
description: Have you ever wondered how a rainbow gets its colors? Join Blippi and his sidekick TABBS on their first adventure as they discover the science behind rainbows!

title: Pal.0
description: When the RV's talking computer system malfunctions, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must figure out a way to stop the rogue computer and restore life in the RV back to normal.

title: Starry Night
description: When Vic and Val embark on a camping trip in the woods, their friends start to act suspicious and strange.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Pony Tale
description: Uncle Grandpa grows a ponytail, which gains him the attention of a magical pony.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Get Your Sea Legs
description: When Victor gets teased for not being able to swim, he befriends a mermaid who offers to help, but at a cost.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: La Cosa en la Pared
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo acusan a Galileo de robar sus posesiones, el lagarto debe cazar al verdadero culpable, una misteriosa criatura detrás del muro, para demostrar su inocencia.

title: Lucha de Pulgares
description: El trío decide concursar en la competencia anual de Lucha de Pulgares, pero una sorpresa obliga a Mao Mao a lidiar con algo impensado… la derrota.

title: Dodgy Decisions
description: Friends and rivals are pitted against each other in a dangerous game of dodgeball.

title: Caillou Roller Skates/Say Lettuce!/Caillou Tries to Whistle
description: Caillou wants to learn how to roller skate./Caillou wants to take a picture of a bunny rabbit in Grandma's garden./ Clementine can whistle, and Caillou can't!

title: Los Opuestos se Atraen
description: Afirmando que es bueno de corazón, Dynamo convence a Axel y al equipo para que lo ayuden a encontrar una batería que pueda alimentar su centrífuga y liberarlo del control de Madtrap, pero Bobbie Blobby no está comprando la historia del malo.

title: Roughing It Up/What's the Big Idea?
description: Roughing It Up: The girls and the Professor set out on an old-fashioned vacation to the Townsville Swamp. Trouble is, Fuzzy and his nephews are there, too./What's the Big Idea?: 20 story high Powerpuff Girls spell disaster for Townsville when they delicately try to stop Mojo from taking over.

title: Piloto Siete
description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

title: They Sent Us a Pie/Dust in the Wind
description: A giant pie is sent to Pretty Big City to stop an asteroid… but the Mechas and friends have eaten the whole thing!/The Singing Stone Heads are ready to perform at the Museum, but when they open their mouths, they sneeze instead of sing!

title: Caillou the Patient/Caillou the Police Officer/Grandpa's Friend
description: While pretending to be a jet pilot Caillou falls down and scrapes his knees./When the traffic lights near school stop working a policeman comes to direct traffic./Grandpa takes Caillou to the park one fine day to meet his friend George.

title: Return to Forever
description: The Forever Knights threaten to use a sinister weapon to erase all alien DNA on Earth unless Ben and Rook can stop them.

title: The Menu
description: The prize jewel on the Secret Joyful Burger menu is a mysterious burger, but to order it you need to know its name. When Larry refuses to tell them what it's called, they go to super-sized lengths to discover it.

title: Drone Shoes
description: Can there exist such a thing as drone shoes? It sounds like they would need a huge power capacity.

title: Stakes Part 3: Vamps About
description: Five foes from Marceline's past come back to cause trouble for the Land of Ooo.

title: Time Crimes
description: When Clarence is convinced he has the power to manipulate time he vows to only use his abilities for good. However, a day at school puts his morals to the test when he's given the ultimate choice to help his friends or pause time in the name of fun.

title: #TheGreenRoom
description: When Jessica is faced with a Green Lantern Corps disciplinary hearing, Hal appoints himself to be her Peer Advocate.

title: Thumb War
description: The gang decide to compete in the annual Thumb War competition, but a surprise forces Mao Mao to deal with the unthinkable... losing.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Big Tick
description: A giant alien tick that sucks planets dry, lands on Earth with the sole purpose of destroying the planet and only a new alien hero can stop it.

title: The Ultimate Bad Seed
description: Malcom becomes the new boss of Blusterland when he tricks Bluster into letting him transfer his inner-badness into a Bad Seed, leaving Bluster a polite shell of his former self. To neutralize the dangerous Seed before Malcom can use it to turn the Silver Lining into a giant Blusterland, the Care Bears must transfer its bad energy back into the only thing that can hold it, Bluster himself!

title: Maxin' and Relaxin'
description: Mordecai wants to get a mix tape from his parents' house.

title: Superhero Feud
description: Control Freak pits the Titans against the DC Superhero Girls to determine who is the best team in the universe.

title: #WorldsFinest
description: When PR whiz Max Lord tells Batgirl and Supergirl he can improve their image by doing publicity stunts, the two friends forget what being a hero is really about.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Older
description: When Uncle Grandpa mistakenly transforms a young boy into a three-hundred-year-old man, he must manage to turn the kid back to normal before anyone gets hurt.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: For Whom the Toll Calls
description: Petunia and Tweety learn how to call long distance and amass a huge phone bill.

title: Stakes Part 1: Marceline the Vampire Queen
description: Finn & Jake hunt for a shadowy predator and Marceline asks Princess Bubblegum for a huge favor.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Stakes Part 2: Everything Stays
description: As the sun rises on her last day, Marceline recalls her long extraordinary life.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: All By Mao Self
description: Mao Mao's desire to be a legend drives him to keep topping himself. But how much is enough?

title: Powerprof.
description: The girls are so busy fighting crime that the Professor doesn't get to see them anymore. So he creates a superhero suit for himself. Unfortunately, he starts cramping their superhero style.

title: The Laziest
description: Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a "lazy-off."

title: Sharing Is Caring
description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

title: Mystery, Incorporeal
description: An old enemy emerges while Ben and Rook visit Kevin and Gwen at college.

title: The Road
description:
This episode takes place when the Bears are young cubs! The three bears, on their way through the desert, come upon a giant warehouse. It's like an Amazon fulfillment
center. The Bears try to make this box-filled paradise their home.

title: Pull Together/Lift Up and Lift Off
description: Ranger Nat is stuck at the bottom of the crevice, but the problem grows when Mecha Abby also gets stuck./Zee is ready to launch his rocket into space, but when the launchpad breaks, the rocket is launched into the farm instead.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: Racer Seven
description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

title: I'm Taking You In/Something Up There/Home Sweet Home
description: When Arlo's mom is out, Lucas looks after him. How hard can it be?/ After hearing a screech from the fireplace, Lucas journeys up to find what is causing the noise./ Lucas and friends find a Gingerbread House and can't resist eating it.

title: Guillermo's Girlfriend
description: Vic & Val try to cheer up a heartbroken Guillermo by reuniting him with his lost love.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: Dragon Breath
description: Bing and Pando are blowing steamy dragon breath outside when they find an icicle that makes Bing's hands icy cold! So they go inside for some hot chocolate. What happens when Bing doesn't wait for the hot chocolate to cool down?

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Pocoyo's Balloon
description: Pocoyo is taking a walk with his beloved balloon when he is momentarily distracted by Loula and accidentally lets go of the balloon. He is flabbergasted as it drifts away up into the sky, and irreconcilably down in the dumps. Until we help him to realize that some things are more lasting than balloons: friends!

title: Who's' calling Me Now?
description: Pocoyo finds a box of unusual whistles. To his delight he discovers that each whistle makes a different noise and summons a different one of his chums. Fun until the tables are turned on Pocoyo and there's a whistle that summons him too. Everyone realizes how silly they're being.

title: Stuck on You
description: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Cousin of the Creek
description: Craig takes his cousin, Bryson, to the Creek, and accidentally starts a water balloon war.

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Just Friends
description: Rigby and Eileen get called away to Don's black belt ceremony forcing Mordecai and Margaret to hang out alone.

title: Ren Faire
description: Clarence and his pals venture to the Aberdale Renaissance Faire. Clarence confuses a medieval play for reality, and vows to stop the evil black knight from getting the princess.

title: Evolucion de Craig
description: iCraig rescata a un renacuajo y decide criarlo hasta que sea una rana nivel 100!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Dance Crew Edition Part 1
description: It's time for another Justice League talent competition and Vibe is joining the judges' panel to critique the moves of the DC universe dance crews.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: The Lady and the Queen/The AB's Silver Screen Debut
description: The Lady and the Queen: China Riot finds a new Bakugan: Barbetra. But this buzzy new Bakugan is a bit timid on the battleground. Riot takes her on as her new project to turn her into the battle queen she knows she can be./The AB's Silver Screen Debut: Lord Brakken and Duran have teamed up and are now the Bakugan film business. They look to the Awesome Brawlers for their expertise in both Bakugan culture and film making to get their movie made!

title: Preparense Para Lo Peor
description: iAxel y Bobbie Blobby se saltan los simulacros de preparación para desastres de Sarge, dejando suficiente espacio en las defensas del equipo para que un cuervo se precipite y arrebata a Sarge! Sintiéndose responsable, Axel lidera al equipo en una misión de búsqueda y rescate.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Answer
description: Garnet finally tells Steven the story of how she came to be a Crystal Gem.

title: Saturday School
description: After creating an unapproved mural on a wall at Aberdale Elementary, Clarence, Jeff and Sumo are forced to come to school on a Saturday to clean up as punishment.

title: Tiara Trouble
description: Bubbles' excitement over being a contestant in the Townsville Beauty, Talent and All-Around Flair pageant is ruined when Blossom and Buttercup become overbearing stage-sisters. But when a mysterious tiara causes trouble for the contestants, they realize there are bigger problems at hand.

title: The Choices
description: When a typically stressful Watterson family dinner pushes her to the edge of her sanity, Nicole starts reminiscing about the time she met Richard. Might her life have been better if she'd never stopped to talk to her future husband and taken a different path instead?

title: Power Punchers
description: Fed up with losing in video games to his Dad, Craig seeks training in the Creek.

title: Tote Life
description: When a hipster grocery store clerk shames the Bears for asking for plastic grocery bags, the Bears realize that eco-friendly tote bags are their way of gaining acceptance amongst the progressive people of the Bay Area. But in their effort to gain popularity, the Bears let the culture of tote bags take over their lives.

title: He's the Sheriff
description: The gang struggles to get rid of the King when he joins them as their new deputy-for-a-day!

title: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!/Magnus
description: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing./Magnus: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing.

title: Opposites Attract
description: Claiming he's good at heart, Dynamo convinces Axel and the team to help him find a battery that can power his centrifuge and free him from Madtrap's control - but Bobbie Blobby isn't buying the baddie's story.

title: Bakugan Wynton/The Boy from Brazil
description: Bakugan Wynton: Wynton has a new device that tracks down Bakugan! Right out of the gate the device works and, Wynton meets: Batrix. Like his name, Batrix is a little batty, and these two are certainly in for a "batty" first adventure./The Boy from Brazil: The Awesome Brawlers are off to a soccer match! In the process of doing so Shun discovers a new Bakugan friend, the boisterous Ramparian, and a new foe in Brazilian soccer star: Pepe.

title: Sick Mao
description: When Mao Mao won't admit that he's sick, he puts the town in danger.

title: Hippoty Hoppity Voosh
description: Voooooosh! Bing and Sula are vooshing Hoppity and Fairy Hippo up higher and higher. What will happen when Fairy Hippo flies up a little too high and doesn't come back down again?

title: #EnterNightSting
description: Karen is given a mission to prevent the apocalypse by DeathSting, a super-cool future version of herself.

title: Rustbucket RIP
description: During a tour of historic Oldeville Ben finds a rare Sumo Slammers card, but when Billy Billions comes to claim the same card Ben has to battle Billy's high-tech drones which have hijacked the Rust Bucket!

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Family BBQ
description: Mordecai wants to get a handshake from Margaret's dad.

title: Hit the Diamond
description: Steven and the Gems play an old fashioned game of baseball.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: A Light Delivery
description: When Thomas accidentally breaks a light he's hauling to the Sodor Festival of Lights, he learns the best way to be the #1 engine is to be honest when you make a mistake.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: New Cat in Town
description: Sylvester is jealous of the attention baby Pepe is receiving.

title: The Deal
description: When Mom wins Employee of the Month at the Rainbow factory, Richard feels like he is never celebrated for all the work he does at home. Nicole is suspicious of how much he actually does, but when Richard goes on strike, his important role in keeping things under control becomes painfully clear...

title: Freaky Gwen Ben
description: When Ben interferes with malicious magician Hex's quest for the earth-moving Titan Gloves at a swap meet, he inadvertently switches bodies with Gwen forcing him to walk a mile in her shoes and vice-versa!

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Come On Charlie
description: Charlie is coming! And Bing has planned lots of games to play with him. But what happens when Charlie doesn't want to play any of the games Bing has put out?

title: Alone Together
description: The Gems try to teach Steven to use his fusion powers.

title: Descanse En Paz Rustbucket
description: Durante un tour por la histórica ciudad de Oldeville, Ben encuentra una carta de Sumo Slammers poco común. Pero cuando Billy Billones reclama esa carta, Ben debe luchar contra los drones tecnológicos de Billy, ique secuestraron la Chatarra!

title: From Below
description: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

title: Grudge Match
description: Ben and Kevin 11 are beamed up to a space ship where must learn to battle together in order to bring down a vicious alien fight promoter.

title: El Ganador se lo Lleva Todo
description: Después de meses de entrenamiento para el Día del Luchador, Axel necesita que Masko lo entrene contra un par de competidores no invitados: iMadcap y Dynamo!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Duck Stuck
description: Pocoyo finds a strange door. When he opens it, it seems to lead to the sky. Every time Pocoyo opens the door it seems to open up somewhere new.

title: Keystone Motel
description: Steven, Greg and Garnet go on a road trip.

title: Stakes Part 4: Empress Eyes
description: When one of her oldest adversaries targets the Ice Kingdom, Marceline rushes to Simon's rescue.

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Hibernation
description: The bears, being an urban bunch, hadn't ever heard of the idea of hibernation until Chloe tells them about it. Grizz, loving the idea of eating a ton and then just sleeping to his heart's content, goes for it with reckless abandon.  But Grizz is so excited for hibernating... that he can't fall asleep.

title: Slobbery
description: Burger's roommate is not only a problem for him, but for Apple and Onion who need Burger's help for something else.

title: The Wrinklegruff Gals
description: Sick of being the tiniest kids at their new school, the girls convince Professor Utonium to create a potion to make them older! Unfortunately, when they take too much, they become senior citizens and a prime target for Mojo Jojo!

title: Gwen O Ben
description: Cuando Ben interfiere con la misión de Hex -el mago malicioso- para los Titan Gloves, que hacen tareas de movimiento de tierra en un centro de trueque, Hex intercambia el cuerpo de Ben con el de Gwen, lo cual lo obliga a caminar un kilómetro y medio en sus zapatos iy viceversa!

title: Major Competition/Mr. Mojo's Rising
description: Major Competition: There's a new man in town, Major Man, a perfect superhero, who cuts in on the girls' turf. But the girls prove that even though they're minors, they're still the major part of saving the day./Mr. Mojo's Rising: Mojo kidnaps the Professor and forces him to give him the same superpowers at the girls. But once empowered, the true evolution of this supervillain chimp comes to light.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: That's a Wrap
description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

title: Pegado a Ti
description: Cansado de que Axel y el equipo lo den por sentado, Masko intenta ser secuestrado y termina atrapado en Dynamo, que está menos que entusiasmado con su nuevo compañero de goma.

title: Receta Del Desastre
description: Durante el festival gastronómico Chefapalooza en las Montañas Rocosas, el Tri-Chefta, compuesto por tres cocineros famosos y villanos infames, persigue a Wildvine con la esperanza de crear el plato más exótico que jamás hayan preparado.

title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

title: The Evolution of Craig
description: Craig rescues a tadpole and decides to raise him into a level 100 frog!

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: Late Night Good Morning With Uncle Grandpa
description: It's the Late Night Good Morning show with your host, Uncle Grandpa!

title: Microwave's Dance Club
description: DJ Saltfish and MC Ackee are in town for two nights only and Apple and Onion are determined to make the most of it and bust some moves on the dance floor.

title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

title: A Sweet and Sour Day/Caillou's Puppet Show/Caillou's Collection
description: Caillou is helping Grandma water her flowers and fill the birdbath./Caillou and his friends Jason and Jeffrey make finger puppets at playschool and decide to put on a puppet show./In the park Caillou starts a new hobby - collecting rocks!

title: To Balderly Go
description: Prohyas is crushed when his good hair day becomes a no hair day and Vambre has to battle a furry monster alone while her bro is in shock without his locks!

title: MacGuffin
description: Uncle Grandpa and a kid embark on a dangerous jungle adventure in search of a legendary MacGuffin.

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Ice Bear's Pet
description: Ice Bear attempts to keep a giant owl-monster secretly as a pet.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: The Paint Problem
description: Thomas needs repainting and must be patient as he dries, even though he feels like he's missing out.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Baby Mouth
description: In order to find out about his family history, Robin takes a DNA test and discovers he's from Babylon.
